<dl id="n40032d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40032d">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40032d"> 32(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> to slack</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The marvel is that the outcaste can toil so incessantly. He shares the oriental tendency to slack and to work spasmodically-to leaven spurts of labour with spells of leisure-but exhibits on occasion a wonderful and sustained endurance. <small> Rev W.S. Hunt, <a name="WSHI1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WSHI1"><cite title="source">India's Outcastes: A New Era</cite></a> (1924) 38</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
